<div id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="heading2">
      <h2>Faq</h2>
      <p>Frequently Asked Questions</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq_slider">
      <div class="slider3">
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="faq_content">
            <h2>Who can use Recovid ?</h2>
            <p>Recovid can be used by anyone who wishes to automate interview process (fully or partially), presentation process or conduct online auditions and talent search. This is especially useful for employers, recruitment consultants,<br>
              seminar organizers, MBA schools and media organizations. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="faq_content">
            <h2>Who else is using online video interview technology ? </h2>
            <p>Many companies have adopted this technology for candidate assessment. Even business schools are using this technology for filtering candidates. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="faq_content">
            <h2>Why not use Skype or YouTube ? </h2>
            <p>YouTube and Skype do not provide the complete ecosystem for interview process. For e.g. there is no automation to present questions, manage candidate list or grade candidates. In Skype, one cannot record and share videos with others, besides the problem that the interviewer needs to spend precious time online with each and every candidate. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="faq_content">
            <h2>Is there any software installation required ? </h2>
            <p>This is a 100% Software As A Service (SAAS). Only a web browser with Adobe Flash Player is required, both for the interviewer and the candidate. This is readily available on 95% PCs across the world. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="faq_content">
            <h2>Which webcams and browsers are supported ? </h2>
            <p>All web cams are supported. In browsers - Chrome, Safari, FireFox and Internet Explorer are supported. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="faq_content">
            <h2>Who can see the video interviews ? Is it secure? </h2>
            <p>The recorded vides are viewable only by the interviewer. Our secure technology ensures that no one else can access videos without proper authorization. The interviewer may choose to share these videos with others. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="faq_content">
            <h2>How long are interview videos kept ? </h2>
            <p>The videos are kept in the system for three months. After that they are archived and can be retrieved upon request. The reason behind this is that interview questions as well as candidate's personality/aptitude change with time. So there is little use in keeping videos for a long time. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="faq_content">
            <h2>How should a candidate prepare for video interview ? </h2>
            <p>The candidate must use an environment that is well lit and noise free for good video recording. It is also recommended that the candidate dresses up formally for a good presentation. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="faq_content">
            <h2>What payment options are available ? </h2>
            <p>Payments can be made online using Credit Card via Stripe(CHF). If the payment amount is large (i.e. greater than CHF 1000), then payments can also be made via an invoice, by giving prior notification to us. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="faq_content">
            <h2>What happens when Recovid credit limit expires ? </h2>
            <p>You will be able to log-in but will not be able to access any service except for the billing and payment service. However a candidate will be able to give interview as usual. An email intimation will be sent regularly on the outstanding payment and last payment date. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="faq_content">
            <h2>Do you provide customized on premise solutions ? </h2>
            <p>Yes. We provide customized solutions for individual corporate requirements as well. We build tailor made software for organizations, which can then be deployed and maintained on premise. For more information, please contact </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="faq_content">
            <h2>Can I upgrade or downgrade my account? </h2>
            <p>Yes. If you upgrade your account, you will be charged the full amount of the higher package and the day you upgrade will be your new billing date. If you downgrade, the change will occur at the start of the next billing cycle. </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="slide">
          <div class="faq_content">
            <h2>What does Recovid cost for job seekers? </h2>
            <p>Recovid is 100% free for job seekers. </p>
